    moved `dog/WHIFF.h` (was `:149-197`) → `dog/git/SHA1.h` (beside `sha1`), byte-identical.
    `WHIFF.h` already `#include`d `dog/git/SHA1.h` (`:105`, for `sha1cp`), so the move is
